    <subfield code="o">9</subfield>
    <subfield code="m">See [10] for the study of the fundamental dimensionless ratio η ≡ τgap/τemission in the context of the semi-classical Hawking evaporation of rapidly-rotating Kerr black holes</subfield>
  </datafield>
